    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【关注我们】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入QQ群：676746738</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在精致的手绘风格的架空世界中开始冒险。您将操控神秘的镰刀少女，探索这座奇幻多彩的神秘都市——“无貌之都”，寻找明日之花变革的真相，拯救异族。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无貌之都：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一座常年被黑雾笼罩的都市，内部的各个区域被分割，只有社会的精英阶层可以通过“列车”来往各个区域。普通居民无法了解到整个城都市的全貌。因此，大众们将自己生活的这个都市命名为“无貌之都。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于黑雾，无貌之都的每个区域都有着属于自己的地貌、人情风格。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【爽快而刺激的连段战斗】</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挥舞象征死亡的镰刀进行战斗。利用丰富的攻击派生动作并自由组合15种风格迥异的技能打出爽快的连段。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193330/extras/901e860b55e3241f7cf19a1c2423fd76.avif?t=1771912313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193330/extras_big/901e860b55e3241f7cf19a1c2423fd76.avif?t=1771912313 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193330/extras/c7ebcd0613fb9e18c6e48ddaa2989f32.poster.avif?t=1771912313\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193330/extras/c7ebcd0613fb9e18c6e48ddaa2989f32.webm?t=1771912313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193330/extras/c7ebcd0613fb9e18c6e48ddaa2989f32.mp4?t=1771912313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【精致的手绘画风】</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有许多精致的手绘背景、动画和漫画。通过大量的逐帧、逐格绘制来展现这款游戏的视觉特色。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193330/extras/24c8d7de7079a20fce5c35824449c8a0.avif?t=1771912313\" width=800 height=452 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>﻿【精彩的boss战斗】</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十场精彩的Boss战斗。直面不同阶段怪物的华丽的技能</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193330/extras/c62e7d7fe7f27284349bfb96f0be1b71.poster.avif?t=1771912313\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193330/extras/c62e7d7fe7f27284349bfb96f0be1b71.webm?t=1771912313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193330/extras/c62e7d7fe7f27284349bfb96f0be1b71.mp4?t=1771912313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>﻿【丰富的成长系统】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天赋树、技能升级、装备系统、宠物系统。在冒险过程中收集材料、搜寻宝物不断提升玩家的能力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193330/extras/f199c7f507c2b9a58d46d487e3bf095b.avif?t=1771912313\" width=1920 height=1080 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿</p>",
